text: Mohnyin District () is a district of the Kachin State in northern Burma (Myanmar). The administrative center is Mohnyin. Countryside of Mohnyin District ==Townships== The district contains the following three townships: *Mongyaung Township *Mohnyin Township *Hpakant Township (Kamaing Township) Category:Districts of Myanmar Category:Kachin State
title: Mohnyin District
